items.name: DiabetesReadmitAI
items.description: This repository contains a machine learning project focused on predicting 30-day hospital readmissions for diabetic patients using models like Random Forest, Neural Networks, and SVM. It includes data preprocessing, feature selection, hyperparameter tuning, and performance evaluation to optimize predictive accuracy and enhance diabetes care.
